Rating: 3
This was a good egg salad recipe. I've been tossing out egg yolks for years and didn't miss them in this recipe. For those that might be sensitive to cholesterol or (like me) not like the texture of cooked yolks, a good substitute (I've found) is to mash up chickpeas. Chickpeas + yogurt + garlic + spices is a fantastic deviled egg filler, by the way.

